OL,3,CAdams v BBC jury 'not expected to
OL,4,Cdeliberate for long'
OL,6,FA jury is expected to begin
OL,7,Fdeliberating on Gerry Adams libel
OL,8,Faction against the BBC on Thursday
OL,9,Fmorning.
OL,11,FFormer Sinn Fein leader Mr Adams
OL,12,Falleges a BBC Spotlight programme, and
OL,13,Fan accompanying online story, defamed
OL,14,Fhim by alleging he sanctioned the
OL,15,Fkilling of former Sinn Fein official
OL,16,FDenis Donaldson, for which he denies
OL,17,Fany involvement.
OL,26,@sD@NrrwD@Yrr
