OL,3,CAdams v BBC jury 'not expected to
OL,4,Cdeliberate for long'
OL,6,FMr Donaldson was shot dead in Co
OL,7,FDonegal in 2006, months after
OL,8,Fadmitting his role as a police and MI5
OL,9,Fagent for 20 years.
OL,11,FIn the programme broadcast in
OL,12,FSeptember 2016, an anonymous source
OL,13,Fgiven the pseudonym Martin claimed the
OL,14,Fshooting was sanctioned by the
OL,15,Fpolitical and military leadership of
OL,16,Fthe IRA and that Mr Adams gave "the
OL,17,Ffinal say".
OL,26,@xD@`OUyD@JO]
