OL,3,CAdams v BBC jury 'not expected to
OL,4,Cdeliberate for long'
OL,6,FIn 2009, the dissident republican
OL,7,Fgroup the Real IRA claimed
OL,8,Fresponsibility for the killing and a
OL,9,FGarda investigation into the matter
OL,10,Fremains ongoing.
OL,12,FMr Adams claims he was subject to a
OL,13,F"grievous smear" while the BBC has
OL,14,Fdescribed the legal action as a
OL,15,F"cynical attempt to launder his
OL,16,Freputation".
OL,18,FThe high-profile republican is seeking
OL,19,Fdamages of at least 200,000 euros
OL,20,F(#168,000) from the BBC.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@PO]wD@AOUxD@KO]
