OL,3,CAdams v BBC jury 'not expected to
OL,4,Cdeliberate for long'
OL,6,FHowever, the broadcaster has argued it
OL,7,Fwould be a "cruel joke" to award the
OL,8,Fformer Sinn Fein president any damages.
OL,10,FTrial judge Mr Justice Alexander Owens
OL,11,Ftold the jury that he will attempt to
OL,12,Ffinish providing a summary of all the
OL,13,Fevidence in the case on Wednesday,
OL,14,Fwith a view to allowing them to begin
OL,15,Fdeliberations on Thursday.
OL,17,FHe said he did not imagine that they
OL,18,Fwould be "deliberating for long" in
OL,19,Fthis case as they will have had the
OL,20,Fevidence relayed back to them.
OL,26,@oD@LOUoD@WO]pD@NrrzD@JOUzD@`O]
