OL,6,FMr Owens said that, in his view, the
OL,7,Fmatters of public interest and fair
OL,8,Fand reasonable publication would be
OL,9,F"more starkly identified" for the jury
OL,10,Fif reference to corroborating sources
OL,11,Fhad been included.
OL,13,FOn the statutory provisions about
OL,14,Fattempts made to verify the
OL,15,Fallegation, the judge said it was his
OL,16,Fview that the lack of references to
OL,17,Fother independent sources in the
OL,18,Fprogramme does not alter the matter.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@YO]
