OL,6,F"Obviously a central issue is how you
OL,7,Fview the evidence of Jennifer O'Leary,
OL,8,Fwhich is clearly central to your
OL,9,Fdecision on that particular matter."
OL,11,FMr Owens said the matter of sufficient
OL,12,Fcorroboration or verification is for
OL,13,Fthe jury to assess by reference to Ms
OL,14,FO'Leary's evidence.
